Author: cedrico0
Text: I know how you feel. Sometimes I wish I'd never wake up too.  But sometimes that darkness passes... And I remember about people that I love. Movies that will be released or othe things to be excited about. About my dog, that I simply adore.   Then I realize I shouldn't try to make decisions when I am on that state.  Please hang in there. You matter. You are stronger than you think.
